"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T16:43:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我無唔開心 純粹好想死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都會有咁嘅諗法，成日覺得自己好無用。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bffa70ebc0dddd42e3166d743d4cbbc58d1c156","tid":363451,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T16:43:47.000Z","msg":"之前會<br />\n但自從發現冇人重視自己之後就冇了"},{"pid":"96a2bfcd9747ca5eda19408d3ea858e1bfe077b3","tid":363451,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T16:45:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88532cbf26d141235b5777c49d7937752d8cbefa","tid":363451,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T16:52:21.000Z","msg":"呢期失業，返工個時一路衝衝衝，冇乜諗其他野，冇乜情緒問題。呢排靜左落黎，認真諗下條career path 反而愈諗愈灰，開始有你所講既感覺"},{"pid":"8268bafe2aa8e38bb08214f2e8bd8d8021bfccd9","tid":363451,"uid":137300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T16:54:38.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成個人都好攰<br />\n已經唔想再理自己唔開心嘅嘢<br />\n好想拋低一切<br />\n因為我真係好煩惱"},{"pid":"fc922d5eb6f681c5645ebe2bc703285fa26bcc39","tid":363451,"uid":121479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T23:37:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前會<br />\n但自從發現冇人重視自己之後就冇了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來因數噉多, 你多數會點放鬆心情？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55268529cc353fa5b59f3810630fd4828490fd5e","tid":363451,"uid":121479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T23:49:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢期失業，返工個時一路衝衝衝，冇乜諗其他野，冇乜情緒問題。呢排靜左落黎，認真諗下條career path 反而愈諗愈灰，開始有你所講既感覺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n失業我怕自己都就玩完，老細一星期炒一個。 下個目標都唔知係唔係到我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d9e9d6415f1ecb4cea26209714006b56d53536","tid":363451,"uid":121479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T23:52:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>盡快搵個奮鬥目標啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n目標有就有，問題我重有年幾就中Sem3 。 成日都諗自己讀唔到書嘅垃圾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9250ccf27df0d5184be54f475a0bcbef323a016a","tid":363451,"uid":121479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T23:58:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成個人都好攰<br />\n已經唔想再理自己唔開心嘅嘢<br />\n好想拋低一切<br />\n因為我真係好煩惱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都一樣，對住啲問題..唔係唔想面對，有時面對到，都解釋唔到問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e98053187e1921669652c71e7639257843ff4cc","tid":363451,"uid":121479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T23:59:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成個人都好攰<br />\n已經唔想再理自己唔開心嘅嘢<br />\n好想拋低一切<br />\n因為我真係好煩惱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都一樣，對住啲問題..唔係唔想面對，有時面對到，都解決唔到問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f1e691e67d05e8eaa42b4828754370675f6e6e4c","tid":363451,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T02:38:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前會<br />\n但自從發現冇人重視自己之後就冇了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來因數噉多, 你多數會點放鬆心情？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食嘢 打機 聽歌"},{"pid":"3deba4e6efe268061b59fb1dc899b11b368ff4b5","tid":363451,"uid":121479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T05:40:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>之前會<br />\n但自從發現冇人重視自己之後就冇了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來因數噉多, 你多數會點放鬆心情？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食嘢 打機 聽歌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日日都做緊，重有無其他？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8318d8e005f07c6f517d39d1ea9472bc03e5d2","tid":363451,"uid":2342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201